data.description: Shenandoah model split level home. Main living area and primary bedroom on top floor. LVP flooring throughout top floor except for primary bedroom. 42" Shaker White cabinets with stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops in kitchen. Natural Gas fireplace in family room and electric fireplace in sunroom. Bottom floor features 3 bedrooms (1 with full bath) and another full bath in hall. Rec room with door to screen porch with sunroom directly above.
